a tvoja sestra Cho-rong.

1072
01:15:05,320 --> 01:15:07,480
Sme rodina.

1073
01:15:09,170 --> 01:15:11,450
Jedzme.

1074
01:15:15,770 --> 01:15:16,770
Mama.

1075
01:15:34,230 --> 01:15:36,590
Pre pána, Dong-gu. To nič.

1076
01:15:36,750 --> 01:15:38,310
Prepáčte. Nič sa nedeje.

1077
01:15:38,430 --> 01:15:39,280
Dong-gu, tadiaľto.

1078
01:15:39,400 --> 01:15:40,800
Vitajte!

1079
01:15:42,800 --> 01:15:43,720
Podaj mi vreckovky.

1080
01:15:43,840 --> 01:15:48,520
Dong-gu, nemusíš pracovať.

1081
01:15:48,650 --> 01:15:51,810
Zostaň tu a oddychuj,

1082
01:15:51,930 --> 01:15:53,530
- dobre?- Áno.

1083
