Nehádajte sa!

1097
01:16:58,760 --> 01:16:59,920
Kde mám vajíčko?

1098
01:17:00,040 --> 01:17:01,560
Prinesiem ti nejaké.

1099
01:17:04,360 --> 01:17:05,560
Prinesiem ti ho!

1100
01:17:05,680 --> 01:17:06,640
Tu ho máš.

1101
01:17:06,760 --> 01:17:09,650
Gratulujeme, vyhrali ste lacný byt!

1102
01:17:10,610 --> 01:17:11,970
Zabudni na to, nejedz to!

1103
01:17:12,210 --> 01:17:13,570
Práve sme to umyli.

1104
01:17:13,690 --> 01:17:15,410
Držte sa od seba ďalej.

1105
01:17:15,770 --> 01:17:17,970
Jedlo máš tu!

1106
01:17:18,210 --> 01:17:22,420
203 dobrovoľníckych hodín. To je veľa.

1107
01:17:22,980 --> 01:17:25,260
Čítali ste to hlásenie?

1108
01:17:25,380 --> 01:17:26,300
Nie, pridali mi ho

1109
01:17:26,420 --> 01:17:29,590
