1110
01:17:29,710 --> 01:17:30,990
To je potom jasné.

1111
01:17:31,270 --> 01:17:33,590
Píše sa tu...

1112
01:17:34,070 --> 01:17:38,840
"Dobrovoľníčka Nam Mi-hyunje
povrchná a príliš úprimná,"

1113
