1267
01:33:16,450 --> 01:33:18,530
Skoro! Tak.

1268
01:33:18,660 --> 01:33:20,820
Hotovo! A je to!

1269
01:33:21,620 --> 01:33:23,380
Daj mi ho, ty bastard.

1270
01:33:23,860 --> 01:33:24,980
Dobre, dobre.

1271
01:33:34,990 --> 01:33:36,270
Tu je.

1272
01:33:39,120 --> 01:33:41,600
